SomniaAgentConsumer::sendRequest
├── when msg.value is less than the platform deposit
│   └── it should revert.
└── when msg.value is greater than or equal to the platform deposit
    ├── it should forward exactly the platform deposit to createRequest.
    ├── it should mark the request id pending.
    ├── it should emit AgentRequested with the request id and agent id.
    ├── given msg.value equals the deposit
    │   └── it should not transfer any refund.
    └── given msg.value exceeds the deposit
        ├── given the caller accepts the refund
        │   └── it should refund the exact excess to the caller.
        └── given the caller rejects the refund
            └── it should revert.
